public class SolveExtension
extends AbstractCommandExtension

This extension provides a command for solving games. The result returned by the solve command will be a map m where m[GAME_KEY] is the annotated, solved game and m[PLAYER_NAME] is the winning region and the winning strategy of the player of the name PLAYER_NAME. The winning region and the winning strategy of a game player is also represented by a map w where w[ WINNING_REGION_KEY] is the winning region and w[ WINNING_STRATEGY_KEY] is the winning strategy.
